{"tid":1782490,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我寧願要港豬父母","createTime":"2019-12-14T04:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T19:05:34.000Z","uid":55623,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7e5258bcc8ccfe8ff7a819ee4b26c6949c80417c","tid":1782490,"uid":55623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:00:32.000Z","msg":"我爸向來就藍到黑嘅<br />\n因為佢喺文革時期長大，好撚崇拜黨<br />\n<br />\n我媽就係淺黃港豬<br />\n但依半年都比我爸洗腦洗到深藍<br />\n<br />\n我哥同我屌又屌過、和平溝通又試過<br />\n就連扮到藍過佢哋都係無用<br />\n<br />\n就算佢哋理虧、駁唔到 甚至覺得我哋講得有道理<br />\n佢哋都係會老閪兜，甚或直接狂屌當自己岩<br />\n<br />\n我爸仲話佢工友同佢講佢全家依半年一齊出去示威、掟汽油彈 每人賺左百幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係癡撚線<br />\n<br />\n日日喺到睇埋啲流料屌返我哋班後生日日上網睇埋啲假資訊、比人洗哂腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呀！！！我真係好辛苦呀對住佢哋"},{"pid":"1193bfb6842b5c142e8ad19bbaba5271101b72bc","tid":1782490,"uid":251769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該推行動post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyqyGMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyqyGMZ.jpg&h=2f6dc79b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6468eb9b480d3343d253920f921a4e0ab464116","tid":1782490,"uid":163704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:01:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"14f8f1797e2307c9880670e55ba1634ac57644d8","tid":1782490,"uid":55623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1193bfb6842b5c142e8ad19bbaba5271101b72bc","tid":1782490,"uid":251769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該推行動post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyq